            <abstract>
                <p>The works appears to be similar but not identical to
                  <ref type="work" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1941Mashaf">Maṣḥafa lǝdatā la-Māryām</ref>. It is attributed to
                <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS5666Jamesth">James "the brother of Lord"</persName>,
                and the bishop (<foreign xml:lang="gez">ʾeṗisqoṗos</foreign>) of <placeName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LOC3957Jerusa">Jerusalem</placeName>.
              </p>
